# {{ project_name }} — GitHub Copilot instructions

See AGENTS.md at the repo root for project-wide rules.

## Copilot-specific guidance

- Build/test/lint command: `just verify`. Always run before suggesting a task is complete.
- This project uses ruff (Python) and biome (JS/TS) for formatting. Match `.editorconfig`
  for indentation and line endings.
- Never suggest committing `.env` files or any file containing secrets. Use `.env.example`
  as the documented template for required environment variables.
- Stage files individually by name — never `git add .`.
